               <idno type="FIEY">8</idno>
               <idno type="BHSYRE">62</idno>
               <sex value="M" source="#bibl1099-1">male</sex>
               <death when="0376"
                      syriaca-computed-start="0376-01-01"
                      source="#bibl1099-1">0376</death>
               <state type="martyr" source="#bibl1099-1">Martyr</state>
               <note>Fiey provides the following bibliographic citations: <quote source="#bibl1099-1">AMS, II, 325-48 ; BHO, 5. Suhadii', I, 357-68. Assemani, ASMO, 144- 60 ; Lagrange, 109- 93; Leclercq, III, 207-19; Hoffmann, Ausziige, 34- 36. BS, I, 42- 43 (G . Lucchesi) .</quote>
               </note>
               <note type="abstract">Abdisho was tortured with the priest 'Abd Alaha by Ardashir, brother of Sapor; Abda arrested with seven friends and seven virgins.  Bar Hadbsabba and Samuel also executed. Then Abdisho and 'Abd Alaha executed.  Buried by Byzantine slaves in a neighboring village. Martyred with 38 companions</note>
               <event type="veneration" source="#bibl1099-1">
                  <desc>The saint is venerated on 16 May in East Syrian church.</desc>
               </event>
               <note type="disambiguation">martyred with 38 companions</note>
